subject: Sailboats and Sailing
America's Cup
lead_paragraph: Emirates Team New Zealand hit 44.15 knots, or 50.8 miles an hour, on San Francisco Bay as the Kiwis sailed alone to collect another point in the Louis Vuitton Cup for challengers.
